{"id": "qlw1665702563726", "title": "$tags", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Struct Functions", "$tags"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlw1665702563726.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">$tags</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: $scalar  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: $scalar  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tvt1665702565278.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:  Development Object and Property Reference \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:  Development Object and Property Reference \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mld1665703024143.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlw1665702563726.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlw1665702563726.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlw1665702563726.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531326\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531326\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qlw1665702563726.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qlw1665702563726.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qlw1665702563726.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qlw1665702563726\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qlw1665702563726___tags_308433\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get or set annotations for a Struct.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__topic_d94385e1_d94386e1_d94387e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94388e1_d94389e1_d94390e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$tags</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__topic_d62832e1_d62833e1_d62834e1_d62835e1_d62836e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1138643e70\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94394e1_d94395e1_d94396e1\">The value returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$tags</span> depends on whether <var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var> refers to a single Struct or to multiple Structs.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Return Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__1\">Return Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__2\">When</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__1\">Struct containing annotations</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__2\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var> refers to exactly one\n                        Struct.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__1\">Collection of references to the\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$tags</span> of multiple Structs</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__2\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var> is a collection of\n                        references to multiple Structs</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NULL</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10418e1_d10419e1_d10420e1__entry__2\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var> does not refer to a\n                        Struct.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Struct Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__2\">Error Constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-84</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UACTERR_NO_OBJECT</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var> refers to zero\n                     Structs</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1151</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USTRUCTERR_NO_COMMON_CHARACTERISTICS</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__3\">Collection of Structs that do not share a\n\t\t\t\t common parent or the specified characteristic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1157</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USTRUCTERR_ILLEGAL_MEMBER_TYPE</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qlw1665702563726__table_d10421e1_d10422e1_d10423e1__entry__3\">Not a valid Struct member type</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__topic_d62837e1_d62838e1_d62839e1_d62840e1_d62841e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1138643e235\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94400e1_d94401e1_d94402e1\">When a new Struct is created, a special child Struct\n            is also created to hold annotations. In the string representation of the Struct returned\n            by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dbgstring</span>, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$tags</span> struct is visible as\n               [<code class=\"ph codeph\">$tags]</code> beneath its parent Struct. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__pre_bxf_rwx_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[]\n [div]\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = element\n [class] = note\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = attribute\n Text can be bold</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94403e1_d94404e1_d94405e1\">The annotation in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$tags</span> Struct\n            can be accessed using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$tags</span> Struct function. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__pre_cxf_rwx_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vClass = MyStruct-&gt;div-&gt;$tags-&gt;xmlClass</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94406e1_d94407e1_d94408e1\">Unlike normal Struct members, annotations have no\n            specific position inside the Struct, and are therefore not counted, or treated as\n            members of the Struct. This is in contrast to, for example, XML process instructions,\n            which are treated as normal Struct members because their position in an XML document is\n            relevant, even if they are not part of the document contents.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94409e1_d94410e1_d94411e1\">Annotations are specific to the format, so\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">componentToStruct</span> has different annotations than\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlToStruct</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94412e1_d94413e1_d94414e1\">When preparing Structs for conversion to another\n            format, you can set the values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$tags</span> to guide the conversion.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__p_d94415e1_d94416e1_d94417e1\">For more information, see the \"Struct Annotations\"\n            topic.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__section_dxf_rwx_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1138643e290\">Setting a Tag</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following code sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlClass</code> tag for a Struct to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">element</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qlw1665702563726__pre_exf_rwx_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vStruct-&gt;$tags-&gt;xmlClass=\"element\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"div\"></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ewl1665702563814.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Struct Annotations</a><p>Struct annotations are descriptive data elements (also known as tags) that are used to correctly interpret data in Structs and convert data to and from Uniface component data, XML, and JSON.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vuw1665702563899.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$istags</a><p>Checks whether the Struct is a $tags Struct containing annotations.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sag1665702563988.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Example: Tags Inheritance</a><p>This example demonstrates that annotations (tags) are also copied when copying a Struct. However, when assigning a scalar value to a Struct, source tags are not affected.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531326\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531326\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$tags Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get or set annotations for a Struct. Struct -> $tags Return Values The value returned by $tags depends on whether Struct refers to a single Struct or to multiple Structs. Table 1. Return Values Return Value When Struct containing annotations Struct refers to exactly one Struct. Collection of references to the $tags of multiple Structs Struct is a collection of references to multiple Structs NULL Struct does not refer to a Struct. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Struct Functions Value Error Constant Meaning -84 UACTERR_NO_OBJECT Struct refers to zero Structs -1151 USTRUCTERR_NO_COMMON_CHARACTERISTICS Collection of Structs that do not share a common parent or the specified characteristic -1157 USTRUCTERR_ILLEGAL_MEMBER_TYPE Not a valid Struct member type Description When a new Struct is created, a special child Struct is also created to hold annotations. In the string representation of the Struct returned by the $dbgstring , the $tags struct is visible as [ $tags] beneath its parent Struct. For example: [] [div] [$tags] [xmlClass] = element [class] = note [$tags] [xmlClass] = attribute Text can be bold Copy The annotation in the $tags Struct can be accessed using the $tags Struct function. For example: vClass = MyStruct->div->$tags->xmlClass Copy Unlike normal Struct members, annotations have no specific position inside the Struct, and are therefore not counted, or treated as members of the Struct. This is in contrast to, for example, XML process instructions, which are treated as normal Struct members because their position in an XML document is relevant, even if they are not part of the document contents. Annotations are specific to the format, so componentToStruct has different annotations than xmlToStruct . When preparing Structs for conversion to another format, you can set the values of $tags to guide the conversion. For more information, see the \"Struct Annotations\" topic. Setting a Tag The following code sets the xmlClass tag for a Struct to element : vStruct->$tags->xmlClass=\"element\" Copy Related Links Struct Annotations Struct annotations are descriptive data elements (also known as tags) that are used to correctly interpret data in Structs and convert data to and from Uniface component data, XML, and JSON. $istags Checks whether the Struct is a $tags Struct containing annotations. Example: Tags Inheritance This example demonstrates that annotations (tags) are also copied when copying a Struct. However, when assigning a scalar value to a Struct, source tags are not affected. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}